      <title>由于交易员撤回降息押注，亚洲股市暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-02-05/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[强劲的美国就业报告打破了美联储近期降息的预期，亚洲股市周一下跌，美元上涨，而中国股市因市场情绪疲弱而继续处于不利地位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-02-05/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 02:05:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着美联储削减押注的消退，美元攀上新高</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-scales-fresh-peaks-fed-cut-bets-recede-2024-02-05/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美元兑主要货币周一升至八周高位，因鉴于美国经济仍具弹性，交易员收回了美联储今年大幅降息的押注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-scales-fresh-peaks-fed-cut-bets-recede-2024-02-05/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 01:25:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
